result.name: CHA LONG 茶狼

reviews.text:
Very nice fruit tea. You will enjoy with a good taste of tea and fresh of seasonal fruit. The smell of tea is aroma and outstanding.
The texture of bubble is chewy but not too hard.
The fresh fruits is quality and variety.

Cha Long located right next to the Central-Mid-Levels escalators, so it's always with long queue.
The tea here with strong taste of tea, when most of other bubble tea shops with stronger taste on fruit.
The size of the tea here is huge, and price is reasonable
The tea is great, but it is chaotic, nobody seems to know how to get the job done, today I wait for 45 min and finally gave up, paid for the tea and left the place without anything...
Very nice for enjoy jasmine tea mixed with some different types of fruits.
Ordered a cup of nitro oolong tea, taste strong and i like it. I think it tastes different from normal nitro but i am not sure if that’s the nitro effect haha

reviews.text: 新鮮水果茶👍

Very nice fruit tea. You will enjoy with a good taste of tea and fresh of seasonal fruit. The smell of tea is aroma and outstanding.
The texture of bubble is chewy but not too hard.
The fresh fruits is quality and variety.
終於試到水果四季春，真的有杞子香，加上水果酸酸甜甜，十分解喝！

配烏龍茶都好好味喎，仲可以少奶～啱我！👍🏼
HK$36 都少少貴🤪
唔差過喜茶，而且更有特色，值得一試！
